data.description: Beautiful well kept corner lot home that features an open floor plan with low maintenance ceramic tile floors throughout. Kitchen showcases closet pantry, breakfast bar, and stainless steel appliances. Master suite with double doors, very spacious, tiled including en-suite bathroom with dual sinks, walk in closets, walk in shower and garden tub. Not to mention, a large covered lanai for relaxing or can be converted into 4th bedroom. MUST SEE! Seller is offering buyer(s) $5,000 towards closing costs or rate buy down.
